<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Hi {{{Recipient.Name}}},<br />
<br />
Revisit Appointment has been scheduled for the Client/Lead mentioned below. Please review the details and ensure your availability for the upcoming site visit.<br />
<br />
<strong>Client Details :</strong></span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Client Name:&nbsp;<strong>{{{leadName}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Client Email:&nbsp;<strong>{{{leadEmail}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Appointment Type:<strong>&nbsp;{{{appointmentType}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Appointment Date:&nbsp;<strong>{{{appointmentDate}}}</strong></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Appointment Time Slot:<strong>&nbsp;{{{timeSlot}}}</strong></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Please ensure you are available for this revisit appointment and take note of the Client preferences.<br />
If there are any issues or adjustments needed, kindly reach out to the Client directly via the contact details above or feel free to contact us.<br />
<br />
We appreciate your continued dedication to providing excellent service and support to our clients.<br />
<br />
Best regards,<br />
Arelia Living</span></span></p>
</body>
